OL,3,CCarer who slapped 97-year-old woman
OL,4,Cwith severe dementia jailed
OL,6,FA Jersey care worker has been jailed
OL,7,Ffor slapping a 97-year-old woman with
OL,8,Fsevere dementia in the face.
OL,10,FDora Vieira, 43, was sentenced to six
OL,11,Fmonths in prison by the island's Royal
OL,12,FCourt after pleading guilty to
OL,13,Fassaulting the vulnerable victim
OL,14,Fearlier this year, leaving her with
OL,15,Ffacial bruising.
OL,17,FThe elderly resident has since died -
OL,18,Fthis is unrelated to the assault.
