OL,6,FVieira was an employee of Lakeside
OL,7,FManor Care Home in St Peter and the
OL,8,Fincident happened while she was
OL,9,Fworking there on the evening of 5
OL,10,FMarch 2025.
OL,12,FThe court heard from one of Vieira's
OL,13,Fcolleagues, Ms Manuel, who said she
OL,14,Fand Vieira were putting the victim to
OL,15,Fbed.
OL,17,FMs Manuel heard Vieira say, "Don't
OL,18,Fpunch me" to the victim, who
OL,19,Fapologised.
