OL,6,FFollowing the assault, Ms Manuel adds:
OL,7,F"I could see (the victim) cowering in
OL,8,Fher bed and holding her blanket and
OL,9,Fduvet over her face, peeping over the
OL,10,Ftop nervously as though trying to see
OL,11,Fif Dora had gone".
OL,13,FVieria asked Ms Manuel to lie about
OL,14,Fwhat happened as Ms Manuel took a
OL,15,Fphoto of the injury on her phone and
OL,16,Falerted the night nurse in charge.
OL,18,FThat night nurse, Ms Prakash, recalled
OL,19,Fthe meeting and said she was told they
OL,20,Fdid not know what had caused the
OL,21,Fbruising.
