OL,6,FHowever, around 3am, Ms Manuel went to
OL,7,FMs Prakash and finally admitted that
OL,8,FVieria had caused the bruise - it was
OL,9,Fthen reported to the police.
OL,11,FThroughout her police interview,
OL,12,FVieria falsely maintained that she did
OL,13,Fnot know how the bruise had been
OL,14,Fcaused and initially entered a not
OL,15,Fguilty plea, before changing it to
OL,16,Fguilty.
OL,18,FVieria had worked at the care home for
OL,19,Feight years and was sacked following
OL,20,Fthe incident.
