OL,6,FIn a statement, Lakeside Manor Care
OL,7,FHome added: "We are saddened by the
OL,8,Fsituation that occurred.
OL,10,F"As soon as our staff became aware,
OL,11,Fthey immediately contacted the
OL,12,Fappropriate authorities to ensure
OL,13,Fswift action was taken - both to
OL,14,Fprotect the safety and wellbeing of
OL,15,Four residents and to prevent anything
OL,16,Flike this from happening again.
