OL,6,F"The employment of the staff member,
OL,7,Fwho had passed all relevant police and
OL,8,Freference checks, was terminated at
OL,9,Fthe time of the incident, and the
OL,10,Fmatter was reported to the police.
OL,12,F"Our priority remains the care and
OL,13,Fprotection of our residents."
